Whether your taste tends towards classic or contemporary, there is a shade of grey just for you. This gorgeous colour has been top of many decorators’ lists for several years now and instead of fading, its popularity has soared – especially since it was chosen (along with a vibrant yellow) as one of Pantone’s colours for 2021. Used in isolation, pale grey can be cold and dark grey can be oppressive, so it’s important you know how to use all shades of grey for best results. These décor tips will help… * Some information from homesandgardens.com; pic from unsplash.com